The marathon will count as a Comrades Marathon qualifier with their 42.2 km marathon. Here is what you need to know: The event starts at 06:00 on Saturday morning at Hoërskool Kanonkop. Entries and pre-entries can be made the Friday evening before, between 17:00 and 19:00 for those wanting to avoid the morning rush. Alternatively, registrations are still open on Saturday from 05:00. The following races can be entered: 42.2 km – R200 per entry.
32 km – R180
21.2 km – R160
15 km R120
10 km – R100
4.9 km – R40. Temporary licences will be available for R40 per licence.